      <div>
        <p class="about-lead">AECTURA operates at the intersection of strategy, enterprise digital products, asset information, and delivery. We help organisations turn digital investment into real, measurable outcomes.</p>
        <p>We don't sell software. We don't provide generic BIM services. Instead, we focus on what actually determines whether digital programmes succeed: clarity, ownership, integration, adoption, and value realisation across the full asset lifecycle.</p>
        <p>Our engagements are focused on defining the right problem, establishing accountability, aligning stakeholders, and ensuring digital initiatives are adopted and deliver value. The firm is deliberately small, senior, and focused — working in high-trust environments where credibility and experience matter.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-values">
