    <h2 class="section-title">Principles</h2>
    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Outcomes Over Outputs</h3>
        <p>We measure success by business value delivered — not by documents produced, systems implemented, or workshops facilitated. Digital initiatives must move the needle on what matters.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Ownership is Everything</h3>
        <p>Digital programmes without clear ownership fail. We help establish accountability structures and ensure someone is responsible for value realisation beyond implementation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Pragmatic Over Theoretical</h3>
        <p>Frameworks have their place, but defensible solutions that work in your context matter more. We focus on what's achievable, not what's ideal.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Senior by Design</h3>
        <p>We don't operate a pyramid model. Engagements are delivered by experienced practitioners who've led digital programmes in complex environments.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

